pistomp-recovery (0.1.0-6) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Start conflicting units (mod-ui, mod-ala-pi-stomp) with --no-block in
    start_main_app() so systemctl returns immediately; the previous blocking
    start deadlocked against our own Conflicts= (systemd had to stop recovery
    before the start could finish, but we were waiting on the start), which
    froze the LCD on Exit until systemd's stop timeout SIGKILLed us.

